      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Dictionary Node Contract\n\nDefines the **legacy dictionary / derived dictionary** surface.\n\nA dictionary may remain on a graph as an inspectable compatibility cache or derived projection, but it is no longer the preferred source of runtime authority for new graph authoring.",
