    {
      "id": "dictionary-role",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Role",
      "position": {
        "x": -866.1515888075525,
        "y": -325.2421704589221
      },
      "width": 537.8633926885486,
      "height": 431.3738869632027,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Role\n\n- Provides an inspectable compatibility surface for node defs, views, and skills\n- May act as a derived projection of bridged and locally bound authority\n- Optional\n- Not sovereign runtime truth for new authoring\n\nIf present, tools may use it as fallback or projection, but should prefer local `_classBinding`, bridge-derived registry state, and explicit local provider surfaces first.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
