    {
      "id": "dictionary-required",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Required Fields",
      "position": {
        "x": 706.7745250215028,
        "y": -258.97886984759896
      },
      "width": 546.0426718907329,
      "height": 205.28234153780704,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Required\n\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"dictionary\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"nodeDefs\": [ { \"key\": \"node-type\", \"ref\": \"/path/to/definition.node\" } ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n- `type` must be `dictionary`\n- `data` should remain structured and readable when present\n- `data.nodeDefs`, `data.views`, and `data.skills` are optional projection tables, not mandatory sovereign state",
