    {
      "id": "dictionary-rules",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Rules",
      "position": {
        "x": 379.3826180582824,
        "y": 1653.9624763170455
      },
      "width": 430.23016738927276,
      "height": 219.39271527619508,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Rules\n\n- Dictionary node does **not** execute code\n- No procedural logic (use Script nodes)\n- Must be readable without plugins\n- Must not be freshly invented to compensate for missing bridge or binding authority\n- `nodeDefs` may project node type to definition graph refs\n- `skills` may list dependency references (not execution)\n- `views` may project node types to renderable view definitions (intent + payload)\n- Runtime should prefer local `_classBinding`, bridge-derived registry state, and explicit local provider surfaces before consulting dictionary fallback",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
