    {
      "id": "dictionary-precedence",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Dictionary Precedence",
      "position": {
        "x": 517.1498361233158,
        "y": 1356.674417038071
      },
      "width": 697.8633926885486,
      "height": 181.33404506770682,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Precedence\n\n- Local `_classBinding` is first-class for bound instances\n- Bridge-derived registry state is the preferred imported authority surface\n- Explicit local provider/view declarations are authoritative for local exposure\n- Dictionary entries, when present, are compatibility fallback or derived projection\n- Conflicts resolve in favor of explicit local authority over dictionary projection",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
