      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🧠 Skill Requirements",
      "position": {
        "x": 501.43993208276197,
        "y": 1041.1489509584187
      },
      "width": 581.8655278916691,
      "height": 216.17858441006774,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Skill Requirements\n\n- A node definition may declare required skills.\n- Skill declarations live **inside the definition graph** (not the host graph).\n- Dictionary `nodeDefs` map node type → definition file; definition declares skills.\n- Dictionary `skills` provides the dependency reference list used by the manifest.\n- Implementations may live in script nodes **in the definition graph** or in external registries, but the declaration is authoritative.\n\n**Rule:** custom node types that introduce behavior must declare at least one skill.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
